<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Crütech Survey</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/master.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1 class="title">Crütech Summer 2017</h1>
    <h2 class="subtitle"> - The survey</h2>

    <form class="" action="submit" method="post">
      <div class="form-block">

        What is your name?
        <input class="required" type="text" name="camper-name" value="">
        <br />

        What is the name of your school?
        <input type="text" name="school" value="">
        <br />

        What is your favourite colour?
        <input type="text" name="colour" value="">
        <br />

        Who lead your discussion group?
        <input type="text" name="disco-group-leader" value="">
        <br />

        What grade are you in at school this year?
        <input type="text" name="school-year" value="">
        <br />

        <input type="checkbox" name="cru-permission" value="yes">
        Do you give permission for your comments to be used in CRU Camps promotion and reporting materials?
        <br />

        <p>
          What email address may we use to contact you?
          <input type="text" name="camper-email" value="">
          <br />

          <input type="checkbox" name="reunion-permission" value="yes">
          Do you give permission for Crütech to contact you about reunions and future camps?
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>How would you rank:</h3>

        <p>
          Whole Camp
          <input type="radio" name="whole-camp" value="poor">
          Poor
          <input type="radio" name="whole-camp" value="ok">
          OK
          <input type="radio" name="whole-camp" value="good">
          Good
          <input type="radio" name="whole-camp" value="great">
          Great <br />
          Favourite thing? <input type="text" name="whole-camp-favourite-thing" value="">
          <br />
          How could Crütech be better? <br>
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="whole-camp-suggestions">
          </textarea>
        </p>

        <p>
          Leaders
          <input type="radio" name="leaders-rating" value="poor">
          Poor
          <input type="radio" name="leaders-rating" value="ok">
          OK
          <input type="radio" name="leaders-rating" value="good">
          Good
          <input type="radio" name="leaders-rating" value="great">
          Great <br />
          Do you have any comments? <br>
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="leaders-rating-comment">
          </textarea>
          <br />
        </p>

        <p>
          Activities on site
          <input type="radio" name="activities-rating" value="poor">
          Poor
          <input type="radio" name="activities-rating" value="ok">
          OK
          <input type="radio" name="activities-rating" value="good">
          Good
          <input type="radio" name="activities-rating" value="great">
          Great <br />
          Do you have any comments? <br>
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="activities-rating-comment">
          </textarea>
          <br />
        </p>

        <p>
          Night activities (One shots, Theme night and show night)
          <input type="radio" name="night-activities-rating" value="poor">
          Poor
          <input type="radio" name="night-activities-rating" value="ok">
          OK
          <input type="radio" name="night-activities-rating" value="good">
          Good
          <input type="radio" name="night-activities-rating" value="great">
          Great <br />
          Do you have any comments? <br />
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="night-activities-rating-comment">
          </textarea>
          <br />
        </p>

        <p>
          Discussion Groups
          <input type="radio" name="discussion-groups-rating" value="poor">
          Poor
          <input type="radio" name="discussion-groups-rating" value="ok">
          OK
          <input type="radio" name="discussion-groups-rating" value="good">
          Good
          <input type="radio" name="discussion-groups-rating" value="great">
          Great <br />
          Do you have any comments? <br>
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="discussion-groups-rating-comment">
          </textarea>
          <br />
        </p>

        <p>
          Christian talks (Download)
          <input type="radio" name="talks-rating" value="poor">
          Poor
          <input type="radio" name="talks-rating" value="ok">
          OK
          <input type="radio" name="talks-rating" value="good">
          Good
          <input type="radio" name="talks-rating" value="great">
          Great <br />
          Do you have any comments? <br>
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="talks-rating-comment">
          </textarea>
          <br />
        </p>

        <p>
          Songs (During download)
          <input type="radio" name="songs-rating" value="poor">
          Poor
          <input type="radio" name="songs-rating" value="ok">
          OK
          <input type="radio" name="songs-rating" value="good">
          Good
          <input type="radio" name="songs-rating" value="great">
          Great <br />
          Do you have any comments? <br>
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="songs-rating-comment">
          </textarea>
          <br />
        </p>

        <p>
          Doorms
          <input type="radio" name="cabins-rating" value="poor">
          Poor
          <input type="radio" name="cabins-rating" value="ok">
          OK
          <input type="radio" name="cabins-rating" value="good">
          Good
          <input type="radio" name="cabins-rating" value="great">
          Great <br />
          Do you have any comments? <br>
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="cabins-rating-comment">
          </textarea>
          <br />
        </p>

        <p>
          Food
          <input type="radio" name="food-rating" value="poor">
          Poor
          <input type="radio" name="food-rating" value="ok">
          OK
          <input type="radio" name="food-rating" value="good">
          Good
          <input type="radio" name="food-rating" value="great">
          Great <br />
          Do you have any comments? <br>
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="food-rating-comment">
          </textarea>
          <br />
        </p>

        <p>
          How would you summarise Crütech in one sentence?<br />
          <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="summary-sentance">
          </textarea>
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>I usually go to:</h3>

        <p>
          School Christian group or CRU group?
          <input type="radio" name="attend-school-group" value="yes">
          Yes
          <input type="radio" name="attend-school-group" value="no">
          No
          <input type="radio" name="attend-school-group" value="tell-me-more">
          I would like to (Tell me more!)
        </p>

        <p>
          Youth group?
          <input type="radio" name="attend-youth-group" value="yes">
          Yes
          <input type="radio" name="attend-youth-group" value="no">
          No
          <input type="radio" name="attend-youth-group" value="tell-me-more">
          I would like to (Tell me more!)
        </p>

        <p>
          Church?
          <input type="radio" name="attend-church" value="yes">
          Yes
          <input type="radio" name="attend-church" value="no">
          No
          <input type="radio" name="attend-church" value="tell-me-more">
          I would like to (Tell me more!)
        </p>

        <input type="checkbox" name="group-follow-up-permission" value="yes">
        Do you give permission for my details to be passed onto my school chaplain/Cru teacher/local youth minister.

      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>Tell us about your Cru camp experience.</h3>
        <p>
          Is this your first Cru camp?
          <input type="radio" name="first-cru-camp" value="yes">
          Yes
          <input type="radio" name="first-cru-camp" value="no">
          No
        </p>

        <p>
          Is this your first Crütech?
          <input type="radio" name="first-crutech" value="yes">
          Yes
          <input type="radio" name="first-crutech" value="no">
          No
        </p>

        <p>
          Did you make new friends?
          <input type="radio" name="new-friends" value="yes">
          Yes
          <input type="radio" name="new-friends" value="no">
          No
        </p>

        <p>
          Did you feel welcome and cared for?
          <input type="radio" name="welcome" value="yes">
          Yes
          <input type="radio" name="welcome" value="no">
          No
        </p>

        <p>
          Would you like to go on another CRU camp? (other than Crütech)
          <input type="radio" name="another-cru-camp" value="yes">
          Yes
          <input type="radio" name="another-cru-camp" value="no">
          No
        </p>

        <p>
          Would you like to go on another Crütech?
          <input type="radio" name="another-crutech" value="yes">
          Yes
          <input type="radio" name="another-crutech" value="no">
          No
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>Which would best describe you?</h3><br />
        <input type="radio" name="describe-faith" value="christian-before">
        I was a Christian before camp.
        <br/>
        <input type="radio" name="describe-faith" value="recommitted-on-camp">
        I recommitted my life to Christ on camp.
        <br/>
        <input type="radio" name="describe-faith" value="became-a-christian">
        I decided to become a Christian on camp.
        <br />
        <input type="radio" name="describe-faith" value="think-about-it-more">
        I want to think about it more.
        <br />
        <input type="radio" name="describe-faith" value="other-beliefs">
        I have other beliefs.
        <br />
        <input type="radio" name="describe-faith" value="not-interested">
        I am not interested in christianity.
      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>Please give me more info about:</h3><br/>
        <input type="checkbox" name="more-info" value="bible-reading">
        Reading the Bible.
        <br/>
        <input type="checkbox" name="more-info" value="christian-growth">
        Growing as a Christian.
        <br/>
        <input type="checkbox" name="more-info" value="leadership-oportunities">
        Christian leadership opportunities.
        <br/>
        <input type="checkbox" name="more-info" value="jesus-and-christianity">
        Jesus and Christianity.
      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>Why did you come on camp?</h3>
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="been-before">
        Been before and loved it.
        <br/>
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="cru-visit-at-school">
        Someone from Cru visited my school.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="attended-cru-school-camp">
        I went on a Cru school camp.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="dvd-looked-good">
        DVD looked good.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="parents-told-me">
        My parents told me about it.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="friend-invite">
        A friend invited me.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="found-via-web">
        I found it in a web search (Google, Bing, duckduckgo, etc...)
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="received-email">
        I received an email.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="received-brochure">
        I received a brochure. (If so where from: <input type="text" name="reasons-for-attending-brochure" value="">)
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="radio-advertisement">
        I heard it on the radio.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-attending" value="other">
        Other:
        <input type="text" name="reasons-for-attending-other" value="">
      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>Has camp helped you understand more about Christianity or grow in your faith?</h3>
        <br/>
        <input type="radio" name="camp-helped-understanding" value="yes">
        Yes <br/>
        <input type="radio" name="camp-helped-understanding" value="no">
        No <br/>
        How? <br>
        <textarea rows="3" cols="75" name="camp-helped-understanding-extra">
        </textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>Why don't you come on more CRU camps?</h3>
        <br/>
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-not-attending-more-camps" value="money">
        Not enough money.
        <br/>
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-not-attending-more-camps" value="away-on-holidays">
        Often away on holidays.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-not-attending-more-camps" value="friends-wont-attend">
        None of my friends can come with me.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-not-attending-more-camps" value="not-fun-enough">
        Not enough fun camps or activities.
        <br/>
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-not-attending-more-camps" value="do-not-want-to">
        I just don't want to.
        <br />
        <input type="checkbox" name="reasons-for-not-attending-more-camps" value="other">
        Other:
        <input type="text" name="reasons-for-not-attending-more-camps-other" value="">
      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>New ideas for camp?</h3><br/>
        <textarea name="new-ideas-for-camp" cols="125" rows="12">
        </textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>Comments about camp?</h3>
        <textarea name="comments-about-camp" cols="125" rows="12">
        </textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="form-block">
        <h3>Note to a leader or a director</h3><br />
        This note is for: <input type="text" name="note-for" value=""><br/>
        <textarea name="note-content" cols="125" rows="12">
        </textarea>
      </div>

      <p class="privacy-text">
        The information collected on this survey will be used to help us improve our camps and provide you with more information if you want it.
        It may be also used for marketing and fundraising purposes.
        If you would prefer not to answer a question, please leave it blank.
        For more information about how we use, hold and protect your personal data, please view our Notification Statement at www.crusaders.edu.au
      </p>

      <p class="submit-block">
        <input class="submit-button" type="submit" name="submit" value="Submit yo' survey">
      </p>

    </form>
  </body>
</html>
